column5: The MSc Artificial Intelligence with Data Analytics course is designed for graduates seeking to build on your existing skills to develop specific expertise in the field of artificial intelligence and data analytics.You strengthen and deepen your skills on the cutting edge of computer science and are prepared to make the transition from programmers to team leaders and designers.
